data.description: Great opportunity to renovate this Farmhouse into your own! Boasting 3+ bedrooms, detached one-car garage, storage shed and a beautiful 1+ acre corner lot in the desirable Perkasie Borough. The main level offers a spacious living room, open kitchen and dining area, first floor primary bedroom, half bath and convenient laundry room. Additionally, there is a gorgeous sunporch overlooking the backyard. Upstairs, there are 2 bedrooms, an open loft space, a walk thorough bedroom or office and a full bathroom. The finished walk up attic houses a 4th bedroom and attic storage. This park like setting is perfect for summer gatherings. This home is conveniently located just minutes from Lenape Park, Sellersville Elementary and Pennridge High and Middle Schools. Nearby farmers market, restaurants, boutiques, and entertainment!
